snippet.textDisplay: I remember Gurdas Maan Ji since m y childhood days. I used to see him perform on doordarshan many years ago.I used to watch it in  our Bush TV (the one which used to come with just 10 channels,in a wooden box).Now the best part is that even after all these years he's still got the same energy and still looks the same thats simply so amazing! Seeing him again after all these yrs in here, also brings back my childhood memories.. and makes me think how wonderful 80-90s era was..the time when ppl were contented n much sober.
